sellerCard.description: Hello, I'm Arvind, a seasoned website developer hailing from the vibrant state of Rajasthan, India. With over seven years of experience in the industry, I bring a wealth of expertise to your web development needs. I specialize in crafting visually stunning, user-friendly websites that are both responsive and optimized for performance. Whether it's building a brand-new site from scratch or revamping an existing one, I'm here to transform your vision into a digital reality. Let's collaborate to create a web presence that truly stands out and drives results. Your satisfaction is my top priority!

description.content:
Hey, welcome to my gig! 


Are you looking for an outstanding, modern, mobile-friendly, and responsive Website for your lab? You've come to the right place!


I am a professional website developer who has worked for the past 7 years for clients in various industries. I feel this makes me the right person to handle your project, whether it be:

  • Healthcare,
  • Diagnostics Lab,
  • Pathology Lab,
  • Fitness,
  • Non-Profit,
  • Gym,
  • Phlebotomy,
  • Lab CRM,
  • Lab Test Booking,
  • Health & Fitness,
  • Clinic,
  • Doctor,
  • Medical Store


Here's what you can expect from my gig:


  • Full Website Creation
  • SEO optimized
  • Lab test booking system for users
  • Easy to use Admin dashboard with personal video tutorial
  • Customize or Redesign existing web design
  • Fastest web loading time
  • Multi Language & Currency
  • Integration lab reporting software
  • Booking form
  • Unlimited Revision
  • Google maps, live chat
  • Security


Do you think why choose me among a lot of Sellers


After Sale Support

Unlimited Revisions

WhatsApp Integration

Get Video Guide


Go ahead and send me a message, and we can discuss your project and the best way to make it happen!


I look forward to working with you :)


Thank you

Arvind Suthar

questionsAndAnswers.question: Q1: What is included in the website design package?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The website design package includes a fully responsive website for both mobile and desktop, appointment booking functionality, lab test booking capability, a user-friendly UI/UX design, admin panel access, security measures, and SEO optimization.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Q2: Can I customize the website to match my brand's identity?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! I'll work closely with you to ensure that the website design aligns with your brand's identity. We can incorporate your logo, color scheme, and other branding elements to create a cohesive online presence.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Q3: How will I receive appointment and lab test booking notifications?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You will receive instant notifications on your email and WhatsApp whenever a patient schedules an appointment or books a lab test. Additionally, you can access all booking details through the admin panel for easy management.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Q4: Is the website secure for handling patient data?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, security is a top priority. The website will include robust security measures to protect patient data and maintain confidentiality. Rest assured that all data will be handled securely.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Q5: Will the website be optimized for search engines (SEO)?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, the website will be SEO-friendly. I will optimize it to improve its visibility on search engines, making it easier for potential patients to find your healthcare and lab services online.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Q6: Can I add or update content on the website myself?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you will have access to the admin panel, which allows you to add, edit, and update content on the website easily. I'll provide training to ensure you're comfortable with these tasks.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Q7: Do you offer additional features or services for the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can accommodate additional features or services based on your specific needs. Feel free to discuss any additional requirements you have in mind, and I'll provide a customized solution.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Q8: How do I get started with your services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: To get started, simply place an order for my gig, and we'll begin the consultation process. I'll gather all the necessary information to kickstart the design of your healthcare and lab website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Q9: Do you provide WhatsApp integration?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I provide WhatsApp API Integration with Standard and Premium plans only.
